name: Darien Henderson
values: Integrity, accountability, and respect for diversity are values that drive me.
interests: Art installations, coding contests, cryptology, mindful meditation, and basketball.
summary: Darien Henderson is a 32-year-old straight man, of black African descent, currently located in Los Angeles but originally from Seattle. He is a Software Engineer in the tech industry and is educated to graduate level. Fluent in English and Mandarin, Darien highly values integrity, respect for diversity, and accountability. He enjoys art installations, coding contests, cryptology, mindful meditation, and basketball. Darien is politically liberal, agnostic, and identifies as an ENTJ personality type according to the Myers-Briggs Type Indicator. He sometimes drinks, doesn't smoke or use drugs, and leads an active lifestyle. His dating intentions are long term, leaning toward monogamy. He does not have children, but wishes to in the future. He enjoys the company of his dog. Darien's potential partner would ideally be a straight woman between 25 and 35 years old, who doesn't smoke or use drugs, enjoys an active lifestyle and also wishes to have kids.
